quran[10{c,v,t}:
32,21,"uss barray azaab se pehlay hum isi duniya mein ( kisi nah kisi chhootey ) azaab ka maza aِnhin چکھاتے rahen ge, shayad ke yeh ( apni baghiana rawish se ) baz aa jayen"
32,22,aur uss se bara zalim kon ho ga jisay is ke rab ki ayaat ke zareya se nasiyaat ki jaye aur phir woh un se mun phair le aisay mujrimon se to hum intiqam le kar rahen ge
32,23,"iss se pehlay hum moose ko kitaab day chuke hain, lehaza usi cheez ke milnay par tumhe koi shak nah hona chahiye uss kitaab ko hum ne bani Israel ke liye hadaayat banaya tha"
32,24,aur jab unhon ne sabr kya aur hamari ayaat par yaqeen laatay rahay to un ke andar hum ne aisay peshwa peda kiye jo hamaray hukum se rahnumai karte thay
32,25,yaqeenan tera rab hi qayamat ke roz unn baton ka faisla kere ga jin mein ( bani Israel ) baahum ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain
32,26,"aur kya inn logon ko ( inn tareekhi waqeat mein ) koi hadaayat nahi mili ke un se pehlay kitni qomon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain jin ke rehne ki jaghon mein aaj yeh chaltay phirtay hain? is mein barri nishanain hain, kya yeh suntay nahi hain ?"
32,27,"aur kya inn logon ne yeh manzar kabhi nahi dekha ke hum aik be aabb o giyah zameen ki taraf pani baha laatay hain, aur phir isi zameen se woh fasal ogatay hain jis se un ke janwaron ko bhi charah milta hai aur yeh khud bhi khatay hain? to kya inhen kuch nahi sujhta ?"
32,28,"yeh log kehte hain ke"" yeh faisla kab ho ga agar tum sachey ho? """
32,29,"un se kaho"" faislay ke din imaan lana unn logon ke liye kuch bhi nafea nah ho ga jinhon ne kufar kya hai aur phir unn ko koi mohlat nah miley gi """
32,30,"acha, aِnhin un ke haal par chore do aur intzaar karo, yeh bhi muntazir hain"
